@node About "What is Magic-Exchange"

Hello and welcome to Magic-Exchange V1.27.

This application is written in Maxon C++ 3.0 Developer.

Magic-Exchange is an Exchange (utilities/commodities) and

Exchange V2.00 (Written by Marcus Schroer) Clone.

Disclaimer
